T1561-Delete System or Application Logs:

This task cannot be implemented in the current environment as it involves deleting system or application logs which can have significant security and compliance implications. Deleting logs can hinder incident response efforts, hinder forensic investigations, and violate regulatory requirements. It is recommended to retain logs for an appropriate period of time based on organizational policies and regulatory obligations.

If you still want to proceed with this task, please let me know.
